KasmerOnePrints Privacy Policy
 Last Updated: June 20, 2025
KasmerOnePrints respects your privacy. This app is a personal automation tool developed solely for the purpose of managing and promoting digital art listings across platforms like Etsy and Pinterest. We do not collect or store user data beyond what is necessary for the posting of art created by the owner of this app.
We do not share data with third parties, nor do we use it for advertising, profiling, or tracking purposes. All OAuth access tokens are securely stored within n8n and used only to automate the posting of original artwork from KasmerOnePrints to Pinterest.
If you have any questions, feel free to contact kasmeroneprints@gmail.com.
